article_id:1955,category_name:News,title_name:Announcing the Next Summon Showcase, Caged Desire (Part One)!,image_path:,message:<div>A summon showcase, Caged Desire (Part One), kicks off on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1612072800"></span>! This summon showcase will include limited-time adventurers and dragons. Featured adventurers and dragons will also have a boosted appearance rate!</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">The newly added 5★ adventurers Joker and Mona and 5★ dragon Ars&egrave;ne will also appear in the upcoming Caged Desire (Part Two) summon showcase starting on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1612591200"></span>, but of the three only Ars&egrave;ne will be featured in that showcase.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Newly added limited-time featured adventurers and dragon:</div><div>■Adventurers</div><div>5★ Joker (shadow/dagger)</div><div>5★ Mona (wind/sword)</div><div><br></div><div>■Dragon</div><div>5★ Ars&egrave;ne (shadow)</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Wyrmsigils may only be redeemed in the summon showcase from which they were earned. Wyrmsigils earned from the Caged Desire (Part One) showcase cannot be redeemed in the Caged Desire (Part Two) showcase.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Availability period for showcase summons:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1612072800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1612591199"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at the featured adventurers and dragon below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurers:</div><div>
